# Copy to `.env.local` (gitignored) and edit for your setup.
#
# Optional: point at directories on disk. The Path tab's file browser will
# show each as the "external" root for its kind, and files under it are
# fetchable — so auto-reload picks up edits automatically.
#
# Changes to .env.local only take effect after restarting `npm run dev`.
#
# PB_EMU_EXTERNAL_PATTERNS=/absolute/path/to/your/patterns
# PB_EMU_EXTERNAL_MAPS=/absolute/path/to/your/maps
